            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Samuel%2012%3A1-13%3A23%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_1%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Samuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESamuel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Farewell%20Address%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Samuel%20addressed%20all%20Israel%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20done%20as%20you%20asked%20and%20given%20you%20a%20king.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_2%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20king%20is%20now%20your%20leader.%20I%20stand%20here%20before%20you%26%23x2014%3Ban%20old%2C%20gray-haired%20man%26%23x2014%3Band%20my%20sons%20serve%20you.%20I%20have%20served%20as%20your%20leader%20from%20the%20time%20I%20was%20a%20boy%20to%20this%20very%20day.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_3%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20testify%20against%20me%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20before%20his%20anointed%20one.%20Whose%20ox%20or%20donkey%20have%20I%20stolen%3F%20Have%20I%20ever%20cheated%20any%20of%20you%3F%20Have%20I%20ever%20oppressed%20you%3F%20Have%20I%20ever%20taken%20a%20bribe%20and%20perverted%20justice%3F%20Tell%20me%20and%20I%20will%20make%20right%20whatever%20I%20have%20done%20wrong.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_4%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNo%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20they%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Byou%20have%20never%20cheated%20or%20oppressed%20us%2C%20and%20you%20have%20never%20taken%20even%20a%20single%20bribe.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_5%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20his%20anointed%20one%20are%20my%20witnesses%20today%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Samuel%20declared%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bthat%20my%20hands%20are%20clean.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BYes%2C%20he%20is%20a%20witness%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20they%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_6%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIt%20was%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20appointed%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Samuel%20continued.%20%26%23x201C%3BHe%20brought%20your%20ancestors%20out%20of%20the%20land%20of%20Egypt.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_7%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20stand%20here%20quietly%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20as%20I%20remind%20you%20of%20all%20the%20great%20things%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20done%20for%20you%20and%20your%20ancestors.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_8%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhen%20the%20Israelites%20were%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A8%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EWhen%20Jacob%20was.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20names%20%26%23x201C%3BJacob%26%23x201D%3B%20and%20%26%23x201C%3BIsrael%26%23x201D%3B%20are%20often%20interchanged%20throughout%20the%20Old%20Testament%2C%20referring%20sometimes%20to%20the%20individual%20patriarch%20and%20sometimes%20to%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20Egypt%20and%20cried%20out%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20he%20sent%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%20to%20rescue%20them%20from%20Egypt%20and%20to%20bring%20them%20into%20this%20land.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_9%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20people%20soon%20forgot%20about%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20their%20God%2C%20so%20he%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20Sisera%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20Hazor%26%23x2019%3Bs%20army%2C%20and%20also%20to%20the%20Philistines%20and%20to%20the%20king%20of%20Moab%2C%20who%20fought%20against%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_10%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20they%20cried%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20again%20and%20confessed%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWe%20have%20sinned%20by%20turning%20away%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20worshiping%20the%20images%20of%20Baal%20and%20Ashtoreth.%20But%20we%20will%20worship%20you%20and%20you%20alone%20if%20you%20will%20rescue%20us%20from%20our%20enemies.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_11%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20sent%20Gideon%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A11a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJerub-baal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20another%20name%20for%20Gideon%3B%20see%20Judg%206%3A32.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Bedan%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A11b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20and%20Syriac%20versions%20read%20%3Cem%3EBarak.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Jephthah%2C%20and%20Samuel%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A11c%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20and%20Syriac%20versions%20read%20%3Cem%3ESamson.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20save%20you%2C%20and%20you%20lived%20in%20safety.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_12%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20when%20you%20were%20afraid%20of%20Nahash%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Ammon%2C%20you%20came%20to%20me%20and%20said%20that%20you%20wanted%20a%20king%20to%20reign%20over%20you%2C%20even%20though%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20was%20already%20your%20king.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_13%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20right%2C%20here%20is%20the%20king%20you%20have%20chosen.%20You%20asked%20for%20him%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20granted%20your%20request.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_12_14%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNow%20if%20you%20fear%20and%20worship%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20listen%20to%20his%20voice%2C%20and%20if%20you%20do%20not%20rebel%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20commands%2C%20t